tu wizard makes the process very easy, and it's a good distro for all the documentation, forum posts and community support you can find for it. Looking forward to loading my server with services, touching on automation and whatever else I can get it to do!\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\"]}]\n27:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Artifacts\"}]\n28:[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://g.co/gemini/share/cc38e037fb95\",\"children\":\"Gemini: Ubuntu Server Static IP Configuration\"}]}],\"\\n\"]}]\n29:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"References\"}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.ssh.com/academy/ssh/protocol\",\"children\":\"SSH Protocol – Secure Remote Login and File Transfer\"}]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://documentation.ubuntu.com/server/tutorial/basic-installation/#basic-installation\",\"children\":\"Ubuntu Server documentation: Basic installation\"}]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://linuxcapable.com/how-to-configure-unattended-upgrades-on-ubuntu-linux/\",\"children\":\"How to Configure Unattended Upgrades on Ubuntu 24.04, 22.04 or 20.04\"}]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.ajfriesen.com/automatic-server-updates/\",\"children\":\"https://www.ajfriesen.com/automatic-server-updates/\"}]}],\"\\n\"]}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"hr\",null,{}]\n2c:[\"$\",\"$L31\",null,{\"children\":[\"$L32\",[\"$\",\"$L33\",null,{\"promise\":\"$@34\"}]]}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[[\"$\",\"$L35\",null,{\"children\":\"$L36\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",null,{\"name\":\"next-size-adjust\",\"content\":\"\"}]],[\"$\",\"$L37\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"$38\",null,{\"fallback\":null,\"children\":\"$L39\"}]}]}]]}]\n9:\"$0:f:0:1:2:children:1:props: